Only portal service is used


npm install moleculer-prometheus

Create project 

» moleculer init project customer-service

» npm run dev


URL
http://localhost:8080/api/portal/portal?customerId=test




Prometheus Docker
» docker run -d -p 9090:9090 -v <path-to-prometheus.yml>:/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml prom/prometheus

example 
Update the target ip address and port in yml files
» docker run -d -p 9090:9090 -v /media/akshith/Others2/ISoSySc/MasterThesis/NewDocs_November/Code/Molecular/prometheus.yml:/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml prom/prometheus

you can find the dashbaord at http://localhost:9090

Zipkin docker
» docker run -d -p 9411:9411 openzipkin/zipkin

you can find dashboard at http://localhost:9411/zipkin

